reviewText: I love  this book and the exercises.  Best exercising program I have ever done.
I have bought all the other Callanetics workouts I can/could get  my hands on. And like the others, this is a good Callanetics-workout.
I had this tape before, loaned it to someone and didn't get it back. It's a good, all-round workout. Some exercises are difficult at first, but you will get the hang of them. Great stretches!
